        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> In the case this is meant to address, can the buffer be re-loaded under the same buffer number?\r\n\r\nYes, I guess that means there is merit to keeping around local vars/mappings/commands.\r\n\r\n> Clearing the extmarks should make sense.\r\n\r\nIf we consider it the same buffer I think we should splice/adjust marks as if the buffer was cleared, not free them.",
